{"tid":953212,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[人間美味] 連登仔最鍾意含非洲豬瘟腸","createTime":"2018-12-23T17:52:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-29T08:00:40.000Z","uid":15696,"like":44,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"7ccf6750df4b03ca02ae850a537727aba6dc5a75","tid":953212,"uid":15696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T17:52:37.000Z","msg":"行政院農業委員會在<span style=\"font-size: large;\">同年10月31日</span>通報了一起非洲豬瘟病毒陽性案例，樣本來自金門小三通水頭碼頭旅客農產品棄置箱，其中收集到的<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">「雙匯 香脆腸」</span></strong>豬肉香腸製品。樣本於10月25日送達家畜衛生試驗所，於30日與31日檢測，認定與疫情毒株（CN201801）吻合。雙匯集團所在的河南鄭州在2018年8月16日成為疫區，但於<span style=\"font-size: large;\">9月底解禁</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kdnVbJv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkdnVbJv.png&h=8075d578&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">即食嫁！屌你老味！</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\ngoogle一下，呢D大陸腸竟然係<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>連登仔最愛！？[b]</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pkWiTXT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpkWiTXT.png&h=e0154920&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/81ecYp7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F81ecYp7.png&h=292e0dfc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">至少五六個post問邊到有得買，仲唔係人間美味？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gZQfWb0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgZQfWb0.png&h=41c9e50e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">嘩 D綠汁爆撚哂出嚟 爆漿呀 好撚正呀！！！<br />\n</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HzGiTZg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHzGiTZg.png&h=38a7fd19&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><br />\n乜出過事咩！？唔理呀！我要含大陸腸！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">[b]媽呀！成班已經中哂豬瘟啦！港豬瘟呀！屌你老母！</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b663aef1bd602721dcfdecd64c661d179bd6c659","tid":953212,"uid":15696,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T17:55:37.000Z","msg":"我肯撚定班人知道出事一定會唔食....<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之後隔多一排又箱箱咁倒入口<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0832eca9e099e06e64deb17c0cc882a5e8c03fd1","tid":953212,"uid":15696,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b663aef1bd602721dcfdecd64c661d179bd6c659","tid":953212,"uid":15696,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T17:55:37.000Z","msg":"我肯撚定班人知道出事一定會唔食....<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之後隔多一排又箱箱咁倒入口<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/lic